@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_miyypf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (tmp * (0.30 - wp.exp(v1 + 0.77)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.68)) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.68 / tmp + 0.69)))
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.34 / v2 + 0.66) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.42)) * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.38) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.13)))
    data[tid] = v0
